07:28.906 --> 07:37.234
First of all, Jeremiah 3 17 prophesies of the millennium, the thousand-year reign of Jesus on earth, stating, at that time,

07:37.506 --> 07:45.498
They shall call Jerusalem the throne of the Lord, and all the nations shall be gathered unto it to the name of the Lord to Jerusalem."

07:46.420 --> 07:56.755
